sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Client/User
    participant App as Main App
    participant PDF as PDF Processor
    participant DB as Database

    User->>App: Upload load PDF or expense receipt
    App->>PDF: Send PDF for extraction
    PDF-->>App: Return extracted data
    App->>DB: Save document + extracted fields
    DB-->>App: Save confirmation
    App-->>User: Show extracted data / upload status